1. if they increase the success rate of all items or even some items once they become "trivial there would nbe little if any at all  loss of coin  this poses the problem that there would soon become an over abundance of plat within norath.<p>

2. with an over abundance of plat in norath this would then cause ppl to be able to by anything any time any place as items would then be to say the least affordable  this then makes the value and nessisity of working hard to earn plat a futile move.<p>

3. money sink quests where originally involved  and enstated within norath  however ppl  figuered how to take advantage of them . yes i realize that some all or none of you have ever taken advantage of a glitch bug or soemthing that could gain you a quick level or coin.<p>

4. with ppl placeing a high value on the items used for the money sink quests this caused ppl to have to go through those that used it in order to do other quests IE the tumpy tonic quest for xp in EFP and the tumpy tonic needed for the string for the trueshot bow.<p>

5. THE RESULT...... well as with everything  in norath  when something has been overly used they nerf it  the FD trick in the ghoul lord room   the tumpy tonics  the fear bug in OT  on and on and on and on  soooooo although we do not appreciate the failure rate at what we do  and we dont think we should have to deal with it  the end statement is that others will take advantage  of everything  that they possibly can if it will give them an edge in the game  so remember  to thank all the jerks that  exploit a bug or a quest or an item  and tell them that thanks to them all of us good natured kind hearted ppkl that want to enjoy the game have had it ruined from their BS actions</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
